Read Some Papers

For each reading below, write a single post on Slack with the following:

Reading Post Slack Channel Link
Visser, B.A, Batinic, M., Worth, N., Book, A. & Toll, E. (2020). Psychopathic Sims: Testing the Cheater-Hawk Hypothesis in a Video Game. Evolutionary Psychological Science 6, 229–240. Focusing on just the measures, what are your thoughts regarding the validity and reliability of the study? #psychopathic-sims
Mathison, S. (2006). What is the difference between evaluation and research - and why do we care? In N.L. Smith and P.R. Brandon (Eds.) Fundamental issues in evaluation. Guilford Press. How is evaluation viewed in your field? Is it generally feared, welcomed, both, neither? #mathison
Davidson, J. (2004). What is Evaluation? Evaluation Methodology Basics: The Nuts and Bolts of Sound Evaluation. Sage. none not applicable none
